text: A viral Facebook post purportedly contains the final words of Dr. Julian Urban, a physician who allegedly died of COVID-19 in Lombardy, Italy.
entity_strings: COVID-19, Dr. Julian, Facebook, Italy, Lombardy

text: An image shared on Facebook more than 1,200 times purportedly shows Italian doctors who died from coronavirus in an operating room.
An image shared on Facebook purportedly shows the bodies of people who have died from the new coronavirus in the streets of Italy.
